Summary: I see an sphere in the sky
divs: Sighting DetailsI was at home august 25 2008 looking the sky, when i see a white sphere, this object was sometimes steady and sometimes moving side to side, up and down, i think it was more than 8,000 feet altitude, after 2 or 3 minutes heads to the east. it went to the clouds, suddenly the clouds open wide and then appears an alien face made from clouds. I have the video but the resolution is low, this shows the right part of the alien face and has his left hand in front his face holding some circle object, the left thumb it���s under the object and 3 fingers above the object. When this face appears in the clouds the white sphere disappears. and after 2 minutes the face disappears as well.
